---
title: Bolognese-Style Beef Meatballs with Spaghetti & Cheddar Cheese | Serves 2
description: Is there anything better than a big bowl of pasta and meatballs? Our quick and easy version is bursting full of flavour, and we
even managed to sneak in some hidden veg! Which makes this the perfect mid-week dinner for the kids.
